Long URL that can be used as sample for passing data to our server
http://localhost:3000/api/recipe?filter[where][and][0][name]=Pork
&filter[where][and][1][ingredients][name]=chicken
&filter[where][and][2][cousine][cousineId]=cousineId
&filter[where][and][3][course][courseId]=courseId
&filter[where][and][4][holiday][holidayId]=holidayId
&filter[where][and][5][allergy][allergyId]=allergyId
&filter[where][and][6][diet][dietId]=dietId

Stage 1
We'll start from simple queries and getting their responses on our react app.
Getting ingredients by name
Getting ingredients by id

Getting attributes by name
Getting attributes by id

Stage 2
Recipe filter with simple queries
Where we have only one item included
Like include ingredient
Exclude ingredient
Include diet
Exclude diet


